Barbara Stock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Stock 0 Barbara Stock (born May 26, 1956) is an American actress, best known for roles as Susan Silverman in ABC crime drama series Spenser: For Hire (1985-1988), and as Liz Adams in CBS primetime soap opera Dallas (1990-1991); she also appeared in the role of Heather Wilson in two episodes in Season 5 of the series.
